div.p: Motivated Care Assistant with 10 years of experience in the Care industry. Offering expertise in person-centred care, implementation and monitoring of individual care plans and management of resident assessments and files. Energetic self-starter and team builder able to navigate high-stress situations. Well-versed in monitoring clients with developmental disabilities and adhering to patient care plans.
